 | style="border-bottom:#aaaaaa solid 1px;" | {{Simple Page Navigation|BookName=[[Wikibooks:Templates]]|CurrentPage=Navigation|PrevPage=[[Wikibooks:Templates/Deletion|Deletion]]|NextPage=[[Wikibooks:Templates/User pages|User pages]]}}
 |-
